    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Items of hardware, often made of brass or silver, including screwposts, brads, book clasps, hinges, book closures, coverplates, etc., that are added as functional and decorative finishes at the end of the bookbinding process.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051190/Lyman, Binding and Finishing (1993)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Materiaal, vaak van koper of zilver, zoals schroeven, stiften, boeksloten, scharnieren, sluitingen, afdekplaten, enzovoort, die men aan het eind van het bindproces toevoegt als functionele of decoratieve elementen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
